fields.name: Apple
fields.about: Apple Inc. is an American multinational corporation and technology company headquartered in Cupertino, California, in Silicon Valley. It is best known for its consumer electronics, software, and services

fields.name: Dell
fields.about: Dell Inc. is an American technology company that develops, sells, repairs, and supports computers and related products and services. Dell is owned by its parent company, Dell Technologies.

fields.name: Asus
fields.about: ASUSTeK Computer Inc. is a Taiwanese multinational computer, phone hardware and electronics manufacturer headquartered in Beitou District, Taipei, Taiwan

fields.name: Samsung
fields.about: Samsung Group is a South Korean multinational manufacturing conglomerate headquartered in Samsung Digital City, Suwon, South Korea.

fields.name: Xiaomi
fields.about: Xiaomi Corporation commonly known as Xiaomi (registered as Xiaomi Inc.), is a Chinese designer and manufacturer of consumer electronics and related software .

fields.name: Dell Xps 17
fields.description: The Dell XPS 16 is a solid 16-inch laptop with a spacious screen and speedy performance that really shines when you invest in upgrading it. However, there are some frustrating flaws in its design that could be dealbreakers for some.
